		<en-US>Cities gain link(YIELD_DISCONTENT,1) over time. Especially in the beginning, this does not require lot of attention, on the contrary: A City that spends most of its time holding one link(PROJECT_FESTIVAL) after the other just to combat link(YIELD_DISCONTENT), instead of creating something useful, would serve no purpose to any aspiring Nation.
		
Several effects increase link(YIELD_DISCONTENT) in addition to the base rate:
icon(bullet) The Laws link(LAW_SLAVERY) and link(LAW_SERFDOM)
icon(bullet) Displeased or link(TRAIT_DEBAUCHED) link(CONCEPT_GOVERNOR,2)
icon(bullet) Enemies attacking the City.

When a City's link(YIELD_DISCONTENT) bar is filled, its overall link(YIELD_DISCONTENT) Level goes up, which increases link(YIELD_MAINTENANCE,1) and reduces link(YIELD_GROWTH,1) and link(YIELD_SCIENCE,1) - and also reduces the link(CONCEPT_OPINION_FAMILY,3) of the ruling link(CONCEPT_FAMILY) of that City. 
While none of these effects are severe enough to cause concern in the early phases of a game, later on the added up effect of multiple Cities with high Levels of link(YIELD_DISCONTENT) quickly accumulates into the dominat negative factor of link(CONCEPT_OPINION_FAMILY,1), which can cause trouble. Especially for Cities with high link(YIELD_SCIENCE,1) output it pays off to try to reduce link(YIELD_DISCONTENT). Options to do so increase in number as you research further into the Technology tree. Note: The link(PROJECT_FESTIVAL) Project is a rather inefficient tool for this purpose, and should only be used sparingly.

To reduce link(YIELD_DISCONTENT), you can:
icon(bullet) Connect your City with the link(CONCEPT_TRADE_NETWORK)
icon(bullet) Build link(IMPROVEMENTCLASS_BATHS,2) and link(IMPROVEMENT_THEATER_2,2)/link(IMPROVEMENT_THEATER_3,2)
icon(bullet) Send link(CONCEPT_LUXURY) to your City. This effect is increased when using one that the link(CONCEPT_FAMILY_CLASS) of the City prefers, and by controlling the link(IMPROVEMENT_VIA_RECTA_SOUK). 
icon(bullet) Improve Relations with your City's Religion(s). Religious Opinion affects the link(YIELD_DISCONTENT) of your Cities with that link(CONCEPT_RELIGION). Making a Religion like you, and making it your link(CONCEPT_STATE_RELIGION) will reduce link(YIELD_DISCONTENT) in all Cities with that Religion. If you have multiple Religions in your Nation, you can consider adopting the link(LAW_TOLERANCE) Law.
icon(bullet) Use the link(MISSION_PACIFY_CITY) Mission of the link(COUNCIL_CHANCELLOR). It can reduce the link(YIELD_DISCONTENT) of the targeted by an entire Level. 
icon(bullet) Build the link(IMPROVEMENT_HAGIA_SOPHIA)
icon(bullet) Construct defensive structures (link(PROJECT_WALLS), link(PROJECT_MOAT) and link(PROJECT_TOWERS)) while keeping at least one Military Unit of the same link(CONCEPT_FAMILY) inside the City's Borders
icon(bullet) Assign a link(CONCEPT_GOVERNOR) with the link(TRAIT_ORATOR_ARCHETYPE) link(CONCEPT_ARCHETYPE) or the link(TRAIT_RIGHTEOUS) Trait
icon(bullet) Train link(SPECIALISTCLASS_PRIEST,1)
icon(bullet) Adopt the Law link(LAW_MONETARY_REFORM)
icon(bullet) Assign a Character with positive link(RATING_COURAGE) to the position of link(COUNCIL_SPYMASTER)
icon(bullet) in Cities with link(CULTURE_LEGENDARY) link(CONCEPT_CULTURE_LEVEL), build link(PROJECT_TREASURY_4), link(PROJECT_FORUM_4), and link(PROJECT_ARCHIVE_4).

The following combinations reduce link(YIELD_DISCONTENT) as well:
icon(bullet) link(IMPROVEMENTCLASS_TEMPLE,2) - with the link(IMPROVEMENT_NECROPOLIS) Wonder, or link(THEOLOGY_DUALISM) link(CONCEPT_THEOLOGY)
icon(bullet) link(IMPROVEMENTCLASS_SHRINE,2) - with link(LAW_DIVINE_RULE) Law
icon(bullet) link(IMPROVEMENTCLASS_CATHEDRAL,2) - with link(LAW_ICONOGRAPHY) Law
icon(bullet) link(IMPROVEMENT_TOWN) - with link(LAW_GUILDS) Law
icon(bullet) any link(EFFECTCITY_SPECIALIST_ELDER) - with link(LAW_CALLIGRAPHY) Law
icon(bullet) link(SPECIALISTCLASS_MONK,1) - with link(THEOLOGY_ENLIGHTENMENT) Theology</en-US>
